Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tidak mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin mencoba mengisap dari leher\Nkarena itu lebih khas vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu merupakan\Narea penting bagi manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada satu gerakan yang salah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya! Di bagian mana lagi\Nvampir biasanya mengisap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dada...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan berpelukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Mungkin dia\Nakan menggendongku dengan mantap...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minumlah sebanyak yang kau mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Sakuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa selalu sangat cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Chiba, di mana kertasmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa minggu telah berlalu sejak aku\Nmulai berlatih mengisap darah Otori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa sudah ada kemajuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah lebih baik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, aku mengisap darahnya\Nsebagai permulaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti memiliki kemampuan dalam hal ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada rapat ketua klub.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tidak akan terlalu lama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat. Aku harus puas dengan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Tidak bisa terbuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kau tidak apa-apa, Ishikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau merobek kemasan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, apakah aku menginjak keripik?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumpulkan yang masih bisa dimakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak keripik di sekujur tubuhmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan itu dan bersabarlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sampai tersedak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar hanya makan camilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kau payah dalam mengisap darah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya ada berbagai macam vampir\Ndi luar sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku sedang berusaha keras\Nuntuk menjadi lebih baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana caranya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menggigit bantal dan makan roti!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja aku juga mengisap darah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga belajar dari buku referensi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untunglah. Eh, vampir punya buku referensi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jauh lebih baik sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengerti, tapi wah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cara makan yang buruk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kehabisan permen,\NOtori dan Eiko juga tidak ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau mengisap darahku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya ini berhasil\Nkarena kau sendiri sangat yakin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore! Selamat makan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh! Aduh! Lenganku! Lenganku robek!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reaksimu berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir kau akan mengisap\Ndengan sedikit lebih ahli!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hampir siap mati karena kaget!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seburuk itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana keadaan Otori?!\NBukankah seharusnya dia terluka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu.\NDia selalu memuji isapanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat lapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memberitahumu ada apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit sekali meningkatkan keahlian...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gara-gara kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan memanjakannya. Beri tahu dia\Ntiap kau sakit sebelum kau mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, tentang itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak pernah terlalu merasa sakit\Nakibat gigitannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kalian gila?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna, bagaimana kalau kau mengisap\Nseperti yang selalu kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah itu bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Ini seperti...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sesuatu yang menenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Eiko, apakah aku yang gila di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu pasti kekuatan cinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bahkan bisa mengisap di leherku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil! Itu terlalu berisiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah leher sangat cocok untuk vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arteri utama berada di sana!\NTidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun, tidak adakah tempat lain\Nyang lebih baik untuk kau isap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lakukanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dada...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jantung terletak begitu dekat!\NKau bisa benar-benar pergi ke surga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Huu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun, kalian berdua terlalu\Nmemanjakan Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibutuhkan lebih dari itu\Nuntuk membantu seseorang belajar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan terlambat jika itu mengarah\Nke masalah yang tidak dapat diperbaiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu memanjakan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak pernah berpikir sejauh itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misa memiliki dua adik laki-laki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak nakal, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau menyayangi mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adik...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau itu! Aku mau itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senior...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senior yang keibuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerahkan usaha kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemimpin jahat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka klub drama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sersan latihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misa selalu tegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia dipanggil "Bu" di SMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}10 putaran lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakuma, kau dan Kusunoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian adalah teman\Nyang sangat bertolak belakang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tetap akur\Nmeski menjalani aktivitas yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, Misa dan aku satu kelas\Nsaat SMP kelas tiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengerjakan PR-ku!\NBiarkan aku menyalin PR-mu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami jarang sekali mengobrol saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shh! Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun, kau datang dari mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lapar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanlah, kucing-kucing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua ini milik kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ritual apa ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berikan cumi kering untuk kucing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Rupanya Kusunoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah. Singkirkan semua itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua itu tidak diperuntukkan bagi kucing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka menggemaskan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusunoki. Kau pencinta kucing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau iya, kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.\NAku juga sangat menyukai kucing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku hanya punya seekor anjing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ras apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pomeranian!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pomeranian...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia berperilaku sangat baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang dimarahi karena mencoba\Nmencuri makanan sebelum makan malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, kau bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, kami mengurus kucing-kucing\Nsampai mereka menemukan rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jaga dirimu.\NAku akan mampir kapan-kapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah ceritanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misa mungkin terlihat kuat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia selalu berkata "apa boleh buat"\Ndan menawarkan bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah itu untuk klub drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusunoki. Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena aku telah menyakitimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan terus berlatih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menggemaskan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gigitannya mungkin tidak sakit kali ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Latihan menjadikannya sempurna!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulailah dengan memperbaiki sikap kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kompetisi seni?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bisa masuk dalam laporan klub seni.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Laporan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus membuktikan\Nbahwa kita benar-benar melakukan sesuatu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}melalui laporan dan prestasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kita sedang\Nmelakukan sesuatu sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu bagaimana tim olahraga\Ndan ensambel tiup bersaing di turnamen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita menangkan turnamen distrik!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Klub seni tidak memiliki\Nturnamen seperti itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi laporan memungkinkan\Nklub kecil seperti kita terus eksis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin membantu,\Ntapi karya seniku tidak bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.\NYang penting partisipasinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sudah membelikanmu buku sketsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kau mulai\Ndengan memikirkan suatu subjek?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah! Apa subjekmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memikirkannya sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada tema, jadi gambarlah\Napa pun yang terlintas di pikiranmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan menggunakan perlengkapan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah ini yang dia maksud\Ndengan terlalu memanjakannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibutuhkan lebih dari itu\Nuntuk membantu seseorang belajar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sebaiknya kugambar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah yang kau isap sebelumnya\Ntidak cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Itu karena\Naku harus memikirkan subjek seniku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa. Kau bawa payung?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Yang bisa dilipat,\Nsiap untuk menghadapi musim hujan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A... Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya payung selalu rusak\Ntanpa peringatan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah\Nmelihatnya rusak seperti ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku harus menutupi kepalaku\Ndengan kardiganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu akan menjadi longgar\Ndan kau tetap akan basah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa berbagi payungku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar. Bukankah situasi ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sangat dekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena payungku kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak perlu melakukan ini untukku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa basah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahumu sudah basah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah vampir lemah terhadap air?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya jika airnya adalah sungai,\Nair terjun, dan pancuran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerimis seperti ini tidak menggangguku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin? Rambutmu menjadi keriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang hujannya deras seperti air terjun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo pergi, Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori, tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan baik-baik saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak boleh basah kuyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bilang tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Ishikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begini,\Nkita berdua akan terlindungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja! Aku sudah melepas sepatuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Langkah yang cerdas, Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini juga membuat kita tidak seperti\Nsepasang kekasih yang berbagi payung.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berjalan seperti ini ternyata sangat mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lapar, 'kan, Ishikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minum saja darahku sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku akan menerima tawaranmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sampai di stasiun, Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudah sampai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa terus tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, dia bilang aku\Nterlalu memanjakannya, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membesarkan anak adalah kerja keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya saja tidak mandi di pancuran.\NIshikawa suka mandi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berangkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terlihat lebih ceria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena ini hari ulang tahunku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku gadis yang sangat bahagia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sapaannya ditujukan kepadaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau, dan seluruh kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pa-Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Otori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ada rapat sekarang.\NKau tidak perlu terburu-buru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semangat, Ketua!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lupa! Aku tidak pernah memberi tahu\Nsiapa pun tentang ulang tahunku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena tingkah sok vampirku\Nyang menyendiri dan salah arah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terlihat muram.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah Otori atau seseorang\Nakan mengetahuinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku menafkahimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalian semua bisa tahu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak pernah menyadarinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada papan bertuliskan\Nulang tahun semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kapan itu ada di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami meributkan waktunya sejak pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Aku benar-benar\Ntidak menyadarinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kejutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hadiah untukmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keanggotaan kafe kucing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiket masuk akuarium,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tiket bioskop, tiket taman hiburan,\Ntiket masuk gratis, Tiket Seishun 18...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu senggang jika kau butuh aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taktik yang kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa, ini dari kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan ragu\Nini cukup untuk mengisi perutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga berhasil dengan latihanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misa terus menanyakan\Ncamilan apa yang kau suka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ingin kau bahagia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan beri tahu dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus peka, dasar bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Kue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gambar ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah Otori yang menggambarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun, Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiup lilinnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap, tiup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otori! Otori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih ada satu hal lagi\Nyang harus dilakukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Burung!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pikir kau bisa menggunakannya\Nuntuk latihan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi aku membelikanmu ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah ini seperti yang kupikirkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Akulah hadiahnya".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita tetap berteman baik, Otori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini boneka Kukuruyuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Burung besar... seperti arti dari Otori?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, sama sekali bukan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbicara tentang Otori dan boneka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantal yang dia belikan untukku\Nsama seperti lengannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Elastisitas ini sangat cocok...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantal lengan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak, tidak! Itu tidak terjadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada waktu untuk bersikap konyol\Nsaat seharusnya aku berlatih!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya\Ndi Li'l Miss Vampire Can't Suck Right,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Nona Vampir Kecil dan Wawancara",
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Nona Vampir Kecil dan Rumah Otori".
